Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), python3, gettext
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/yeager/vsdview

Package: vsdview
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-gi, libvisio-ng (>= 0.6.0), gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1, gir1.2-rsvg-2.0, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: librsvg2-bin
Description: Read-only viewer for Microsoft Visio files
 VSDView is a read-only viewer for Microsoft Visio files (.vsdx and .vsd),
 built with GTK4 and libadwaita. Uses libvisio-ng for native Visio file
 parsing — no external dependencies needed.
